### **3. 25_LogBurstSignal**  
**Description:**  
Detects bursty and repetitive log patterns with heatmap-style frequency detection.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogBurstSignal - Log Spike and Repetition Detector

LogBurstSignal helps identify noisy log segments and repeated errors that can indicate instability or performance issues.

## Features
- Keyword clustering  
- Burst and repetition mapping  
- CLI and timeline filters  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_LogBurstSignal.git
cd 25_LogBurstSignal
python analyze.py
